item.title: By: mrs_orr2000
item.dc:creator: mrs_orr2000
item.description: Remember my old phone camera lens problem? I just saw a hack on fb to use transparent glossy tape on lens. I hurried to try but it made no difference so I took it off. Voila! It was fixed!
